data.description: Lovely home near many Spring Hill Amenities and approximately 45 minutes to Tampa and Tampa International Airport! New Porcelain Tile throughout home - No Carpet!  Florida room has windows, new screens and new carpet for peaceful indoor/outdoor relaxation. Interior vents Cleaned and Repaired 2022! Exterior and Interior paint 2023.  All New, beautiful, Wide Woodwork and Crown Molding 2023. New Hardware installed on front door, closets, sinks, interior doors and kitchen cabinets 2023! Homes Invites you in through a Beautiful entry door. Other improvements are Roof 2012, Air Conditioner 2015, Stove and Fridge 2021, Microwave and Dishwasher 2023! All Electrical Outlets and Switch Plates replaced 2022. Interior and Exterior Electrical boxes 2021. Many new light fixtures. Large Backyard Shed! Great Carport with Attached Storage Shed - could be enclosed!  Leaf Filters on Gutters. New vanity in   Bath. New blinds! Lovely new Chimes and Door Bell!  Fenced Yard. A truly must see to appreciate!
